洪灾害可能性较大（黄色预警），保定西部等地局地可能发生山洪灾害（蓝色预警）。请上述地区注意做好实时监测、防汛预警和转移避险等防范工作。 河北省气象台 7 月 21 日 14 时发布天气实况：20 日 20 时 -21 日 14 时，承德南部、唐山大部、秦皇岛南部、保定、雄安新区、廊坊西部、沧州西部、石家庄、衡水、邢台、邯郸等地出现降雨，降雨区平均降雨量为 33.7 毫米，保定中南部、石家庄西部和南部、邢台中西部、邯郸等地共有 610 个站点降雨量超过 50 毫米（暴雨），其中石家庄西部和南部、邢台中西部、邯郸等地有 98 个站点降雨量在 100 毫米以上（大暴雨），邱县的陈村乡最大为 208.6 毫米（大暴雨），易县的尉都小时雨强最大为 84.9 毫米。石家庄主城区降雨量在 24.7 毫米 (中雨)-94.3 毫米 (暴雨)，桥西污水处理厂最大。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f14d30b4a3a2bc44a352e516be337dc7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "77 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/473789442"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Igo6/8Ymj4b5+EAMaCDY3NTY2Mzg5IMXz34cGMAI4kQFAHHIJNDczNzg5NDQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1626969778.4198656", "card_id": "Q_470974760", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "哪些诗句让你念念不忘？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-30ccb412f4d1e3e4e4375113b0cdea4b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "75 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/470974760"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Igo6/8Ymj4b5+EAMaCDY2OTQwNjEzIL3im4cGMAA4gAJAHXIJNDcwOTc0NzYweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1626969778.4201488", "card_id": "Q_472268185", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 191}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么很羡慕别人谈恋爱，自己却不想谈恋爱？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/472268185"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Igo6/8Ymj4b5+EAMaCDY3MjI3ODkxIP/zu4cGMAA42AFAHnIJNDcyMjY4MTg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style